=== locked_door ===
~ triggerMonologue("logic", 5, "Three deadbolts. Someone really doesn't want you through here.")
~ triggerMonologue("perception", 6, "Fresh scratches around the keyhole. This has been picked before.")
The door is locked. Three deadbolts, all thrown.
